UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 2444
1 AN ACT relating to public protection.
2 Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of Kentucky:
3 Section 1. KRS 65.8925 is amended to read as follows:
4 (1) [By January 1, 2012, ]The commissioners of a regional wastewater commission
5 established under the provisions of KRS 65.8901 to 65.8923 shall provide public
6 access to records relating to expenditures of the commission through display of the
7 records on a website[Web site].
8 (2) The website[Web site] shall be in a searchable format and shall provide financial
9 information about expenditures not exempt under the provisions of state or federal
10 law, including:
11 (a) The payee name;
12 (b) The category or type of expenditure;
13 (c) A description of the reason for the expenditure, if available;
14 (d) The expenditure amount;
15 (e) An electronic link to documents relating to the expenditure, if the documents
16 are available electronically;
17 (f) The budget adopted by the commission and subsequent amendments to that
18 budget;
19 (g) The completed annual audit results; and
20 (h) Any other information deemed relevant by the commission.
21 (3) Information on the website[Web site] shall be updated at least on a monthly basis
22 and shall be maintained on the website[Web site] for at least three (3) years.
23 (4) (a) The regional wastewater commission shall register with the Department for
24 Local Government as required by KRS 65A.090.
25 (b) [For fiscal periods beginning on and after July 1, 2014, ]The provisions of
26 KRS 65A.010 to 65A.090 shall apply to regional wastewater commissions.
27 Commissioners shall work with the Department for Local Government to
